# Testing Guide

## Unit Tests
- Use JUnit5
- All ViewModels must have unit tests
- All UseCases must have unit tests
- Use Given-When-Then format
- Mock dependencies with Mockk library

## UI Tests
- Use ComposeTestRule
- Each screen must have at least 1 UI test
- Prioritize semantics testing
- Screenshot testing recommended

## Test Coverage
- Domain Layer: 90% or higher
- Data Layer: 80% or higher
- Presentation Layer: 70% or higher

## Performance Testing
- Compose recomposition optimization tests
- Memory leak tests (LeakCanary)
- Frame drop monitoring
